Lifelong Learning Societies<\/strong> in the Asia-Pacific.<\/p>\n<p>An avid believer and strong proponent of 21<sup>st<\/sup> Century Skills, in 2010, he presented a paper on \u201c<strong>Use of technology to build 21st century skills in formal education\u201d<\/strong> during <strong>Massachusetts Institute of Technology (MIT),<\/strong> (USA) Learning International Networks Consortium (LINC) Conference.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/section><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-4703","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/compudonjunior.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/4703","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/compudonjunior.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/compudonjunior.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/compudonjunior.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/compudonjunior.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4703"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/compudonjunior.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/4703\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4705,"href":"https:\/\/compudonjunior.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/4703\/revisions\/4705"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/compudonjunior.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4703"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}